bool corresponds (Hash_table_item &saved_, Hash_table_item &new_)

Detailed Description

Contains implementation of methods related to tree searching ( page_3 ).

In this file important methods performing tree searching ( or related to tree searching ) are implemented. Tree searching itself ( T_searcher::search ) is done with standart minimax algorithm.
